03:42.022 --> 03:44.024
Well, I'm gonna look it up!

03:44.024 --> 03:46.560
Well, see you, Officer.

03:46.560 --> 03:49.797
I'll tell you,
that guy's got some nerve.

03:49.797 --> 03:51.632
