06:25.452 --> 06:28.221
I got a lot more ties to sell.

06:28.221 --> 06:29.422
Yeah, Fonz?

06:29.423 --> 06:31.792
School is your business now.

06:31.792 --> 06:33.759
Oh, Fonz, I can't.

06:33.760 --> 06:34.961
I need the loot.

06:34.962 --> 06:36.829
I got to help out at home.

06:36.830 --> 06:39.066
All right, here's the plan.

06:39.066 --> 06:41.400
You do good in school,
you show me good grades,

06:41.401 --> 06:44.104
I'll give you a part-time job
with me at the garage.

06:44.104 --> 06:46.640
- You mean it?
- Hey, I'm a man of my word.

06:46.640 --> 06:49.241
Boy, working side by side
with you, Fonz.

06:49.242 --> 06:50.376
You got a deal.

06:50.377 --> 06:52.346
All right.

06:52.346 --> 06:54.348
- Hey, thanks, Richie.
- Oh, it's all right.

06:54.348 --> 06:55.948
Now, what do you think
Joanie's gonna want

06:55.949 --> 06:57.184
