great on you, Mr. C.

07:07.194 --> 07:09.526
Yeah, it's my favorite color.

07:13.066 --> 07:15.468
Well...

07:15.469 --> 07:17.838
I'm ready.

07:17.838 --> 07:18.872
Hi-ya, Blue Eyes.

07:18.872 --> 07:20.707
Wah-wah-wah.

07:20.707 --> 07:23.109
