07:34.321 --> 07:36.023
Aw, Dad, I can't.

07:36.023 --> 07:38.492
I... I'm going with Laurie Beth.
I promised her.

07:38.492 --> 07:41.595
We're gonna go out and take
a little moonlight stroll.

07:41.595 --> 07:43.330
Do it in the morning.

07:43.330 --> 07:46.300
Aw, you're a real
joker, Dad. He's...

07:49.036 --> 07:51.370
All right, Chachi,
let's get started.

07:51.371 --> 07:53.362
I teach, you learn.

07:59.913 --> 08:01.214
Dad, please.

08:01.214 --> 08:04.117
All right, Joanie,
I can see you're in charge.

08:04.117 --> 08:07.854
But I'll be at the top of the
stairs listening for your call.

08:07.854 --> 08:10.846
A simple "help" will do.

08:12.626 --> 08:14.294
All right,
you're behind at school,

08:14.294 --> 08:16.229
