to the heavy stuff?

08:23.537 --> 08:27.741
You want a broken nose first
or go right on to the hospital?

08:27.741 --> 08:29.476
You got spirit.

08:29.476 --> 08:30.777
I love older women.

08:30.777 --> 08:32.379
Let's run away together.

08:32.379 --> 08:34.448
How far can we run?

08:34.448 --> 08:36.750
You got to be in by 10:00.

08:36.750 --> 08:41.051
Now, we either begin to study
or I will call my father.

08:41.988 --> 08:43.456
And then I'll call Fonzie.

08:43.457 --> 08:44.957
- Oh, right, uh...
- Yeah.

08:44.958 --> 08:47.861
I have a test tomorrow, and
here are some sample questions.

