to a marching band?

09:46.153 --> 09:48.288
Not ties,
I got a hundred on my test.

09:48.288 --> 09:49.556
A perfect score.

09:49.556 --> 09:50.991
Are you snowing me?

09:50.991 --> 09:51.992
No.

09:51.992 --> 09:53.859
Hey, your Fonzarelli blood

09:53.860 --> 09:55.829
finally made it
up to your brain, huh?

09:55.829 --> 09:57.764
I'm proud of you,
I'm proud of you.

09:57.764 --> 09:59.399
All right, Chachi, all right.

09:59.399 --> 10:01.635
You got a job.

