11:02.362 --> 11:03.630
- Well, it's what she said.
- JOANIE: Yeah.

11:03.630 --> 11:05.497
And he's been suspended
for two weeks.

11:05.498 --> 11:07.500
A suspended head in my hat?

11:07.500 --> 11:09.669
Pretty good, huh?

11:09.669 --> 11:10.670
Hi-ya, Blue Eyes.

11:10.670 --> 11:12.661
How do you like it?

11:13.740 --> 11:15.731
Wah-wah-wah!

11:17.577 --> 11:19.145
