11:29.389 --> 11:31.258
That hundred?
You cheated, didn't you?

11:31.258 --> 11:32.891
So?

11:32.892 --> 11:35.395
So?! My cousin don't cheat!

11:35.395 --> 11:37.497
What do you got to say
besides "so"?!

11:37.497 --> 11:39.899
- What do I got to say?
- Yeah.

11:39.899 --> 11:41.334
I'll tell you what.

11:41.334 --> 11:42.602
I don't need your stinking job!

11:42.602 --> 11:44.204
I've been doing
all right without it!

11:44.204 --> 11:46.373
Without you, without school,
without anybody!

11:46.373 --> 11:48.540
And I'll tell you
something else, Fonzarelli.

11:48.541 --> 11:50.532
I don't need your stupid cap!

11:53.647 --> 11:55.376
"Stupid can"?

11:56.383 --> 11:58.385
"Stupid cap"?!

11:58.385 --> 12:01.787
